      { type: "p", text: `Illustration 4: The Blended Margin Illusion (For Chapter 3)\nVisual: A simple pie chart or bar graph divided into two starkly contrasting sections.\nDesign: A small 20% slice colored deep green, labelled: The Core Niche (High Margin, Low Chaos). The massive 80% remaining slice is colored red or grey, labelled: The Distractions (Low Margin, High Chaos).\nCaption: Your good customers are subsidising the exhaustion caused by your bad customers.` },
