      { type: "p", text: `Image 15: The Strategic Moat (For Chapter 9: The Beginning of Strategy)\nVisual Concept: A highly complex, specialized industrial part (like a medical wiring harness or an aerospace bracket) resting safely inside a heavy, impenetrable medieval fortress wall.\nCaption: True strategy doesn't just win you a premium order; it builds an uncopyable fortress around your margins.` }
